keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
map <c-l> nextTab
map <c-h> previousTab
map H previousTab
map L nextTab
map b Vomnibar.activateBookmarksInNewTab
map B Vomnibar.activateBookmarksInNewTab
map gb goBack
map gf goForward
map gp visitPreviousTab
map h LinkHints.activateMode action=hover
map H LinkHints.activateMode action=focus
map c LinkHints.activateMode action=copy-text
map ' Marks.activateGotoMode
map R reload hard
map t Vomnibar.activateTabSelection
map <space> enterFindMode
map <enter> Vomnibar.activateInNewTab
map <left> previousTab
map <right> nextTab
map <down> scrollToBottom
map <up> scrollToTop
searchEngines:
w: https://www.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Search&search=%s Wikipedia
